Resistance is futile.

Utility: lsiommu

  Lists IOMMU isolation groups and the devices that belong there.

Utility: lssriov

  Lists virtual functions (SR-IOV) of network devices and the IOMMU isolation
  groups they belong to.

Utility: lsusbpci

  Lists USB devices along with their /sys/devices/pci... locations.

Utility: rebind

  Rebinds a PCIe device from its original driver to vfio-pci. 

